title: JU students secure runner-up position at State level Hackathon
description: Excelsior Sports Correspondent JAMMU, Nov 12: Students from the University of Jammu’s “Design Your Degree” (DYD) B.Tech programme in Artificial Intelligence & Mathematical Innovations have secured the runner-up position at a State level Hackathon organized by Islamic University of Science & Technology (IUST), Awantipora. The winning seven member team consisted of Adil Mahajan, Tavishi Amla, Pawandeep Singh, Bhoomi Samnotra, Avichal Badyal, Gourav Sharma and Suhani Behl.
